<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>Sticky Lessons - Personal Growth Journey</title>
		<style>
			body {
				font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
				max-width: 800px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 2rem;
				line-height: 1.6;
			}
			.hero {
				padding: 2rem 0;
				border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
			}
			.systems {
				display: grid;
				gap: 2rem;
				padding: 2rem 0;
			}
			.system-card {
				padding: 1.5rem;
				border: 1px solid #eee;
				border-radius: 8px;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<main>
			<section class="hero">
				<h1>Sticky Lessons</h1>
				<p>A documentation of my 2025 journey in personal and professional growth.</p>
			</section>

			<section class="systems">
				<div class="system-card">
					<h2>🏠 Become the Rock</h2>
					<p>Establishing myself as a core pillar in my family structure through:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Home ownership and family </li>
						<li>AWS cloud </li>
						<li>Family leadership</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="system-card">
					<h2>💪 Sharpen the Vessel</h2>
					<p>Personal growth through physical challenge:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Martial Arts</li>
						<li>Injury prevention and management</li>
					
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="system-card">
					<h2>🌱 Plant the Tree</h2>
					<p>Building lasting value for the future:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Monthly blog publications</li>
						<li>Technical knowledge documentation</li>
						<li>Small business development</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>